<p>University (academia) does exist (and always has).  It&#8217;s just moved up to (real) &#8220;postgraduate&#8221; degrees.</p>

<p>University (or college as I think Americans call it) is now just &#8220;Tertiary School.&#8221;</p>

<p>Long live real academia!</p>

